---
layout: base.njk
title: 标签索引
description: 所有标签和对应文章。
permalink: /tags/index.html
---
<section class="archive-head">
  <p class="eyebrow">全部标签</p>
  <h1>标签索引</h1>
  <p>标签会根据文章自动生成，适合整理小说、学习、随笔和折腾记录。</p>
</section>

{% set tags = collections.all | tagList %}
<section class="tag-cloud">
{% for tag in tags %}
  <a href="#{{ tag | urlencode }}">{{ tag }}</a>
{% endfor %}
</section>

<section class="tag-sections">
{% for tag in tags %}
  <div class="tag-section" id="{{ tag | urlencode }}">
    <h2>{{ tag }}</h2>
    {% for post in collections.posts | postsByTag(tag) %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}"><span>{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
{% endfor %}
</section>
